Package: GetDFPData
Title: Reading Quarterly Financial Statements from Bovespa
Version: 0.5
Date: 2017-09-29
Authors@R: person("Marcelo", "Perlin", email = "marceloperlin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reads quarterly financial statements including assets, liabilities, income and many more from Bovespa DFP system.
 The package is specially designed for large scale data, keeping a tabular (long) structure for easier processing. 
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports: stringr,XML,dplyr, readr, reshape2, tibble, xlsx, stats, curl
License: GPL-2
BugReports: https://github.com/msperlin/GetDFPData/issues
URL: https://github.com/msperlin/GetDFPData/
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat,
    ggplot2
VignetteBuilder: knitr
